OL,3,CViktor Orban concedes defeat in
OL,4,C'painful' Hungarian election
OL,6,FHungarian Prime Minister Viktor Orban
OL,7,Fhas conceded defeat in the general
OL,8,Felection, ending 16 years of
OL,9,Fcontroversial rule that saw him become
OL,10,Fa favourite of Donald Trump and
OL,11,FValdimir Putin.
OL,13,F"I congratulated the victorious
OL,14,Fparty, Orban told supporters in
OL,15,FBudapest. "We are going to serve the
OL,16,FHungarian nation and our homeland from
OL,17,Fopposition as well."
OL,19,FInitial official results show
OL,20,Fopposition leader Peter Magyar's party
OL,21,Fdominating the election.
OL,26,@kD@KrpnD@drpuD@AOUvD@LrpwD@KOUyD@TO]
