OL,3,CViktor Orban concedes defeat in
OL,4,C'painful' Hungarian election
OL,6,FMagyar posted on Facebook that "Prime
OL,7,FMinister Viktor Orban just
OL,8,Fcongratulated me on the phone on our
OL,9,Fvictory."
OL,11,FIt brings to an end the Orban era of
OL,12,Fgovernment, which saw him remain near
OL,13,Fconstantly at odds with the European
OL,14,FUnion.
OL,16,FHe repeatedly frustrated EU efforts to
OL,17,Fsupport Ukraine in its war against
OL,18,FRussia's full-scale invasion, while
OL,19,Fcultivating close ties to Putin and
OL,20,Frefusing to end Hungary's dependence
OL,21,Fon Russian fossil fuel imports.
